sections.comments: Please contact academic.support@nursing.ubc.ca to register in this section.Students in the MSN program may complete the program requirements by completing a MSN SPAR Project (NURS 595  Scholarly Practice Advancement Research project (SPAR), 3 credits). Typically, students register for this option from the first term of enrolment into the program and work on the SPAR alongside the completion of their required and optional course work (30 credits).
